      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to own! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. It looks great, drives smoothly, and is totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. If you're looking for a dependable car that still has plenty of life and looks the part, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
