    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies (ITBs) and a crisp dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that has been recently overhauled. Torque is managed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and delivered to the pavement via a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is bolstered by a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure for this platform\u2014and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its enthusiast use, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive cooling system refresh. This is a communicative, analog driving machine tuned for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
