    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-maintained performance machine that balances luxury with everyday reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor, expected road-wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seating is supple and intact, and every electronic feature\u2014from the intuitive navigation system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound, having undergone regular professional servicing, which is evident in its smooth acceleration and responsive handling. It\u2019s a complete package for a discerning driver who values both aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity.",
